(A)     NON-CASH CHARGES TO EARNINGS AS PRESENTED HERE CONSIST OF DEPRECIATION,

IN-PROCESS RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT, AMORTIZATION, RETIREE HEALTH CARE

