ADDITIONAL INFUSIONS FROM THE PARTNERS DURING 2001.  THIS IS EXPECTED

TO RESULT IN ADDITIONAL CASH REQUIREMENTS AND-OR LOAN GUARANTEES

IMPOSED ON THE COMPANY.

